# Regression for kinetic-theory flux with timestep chosen from mapped flux.

units               si

voxel_material      carbon density 1800.0
voxel_create        solid sphere diameter 1.0e-3 resolution 10 material carbon
source              unused constant 0.0 units kg/m2/s
iac_timestep        1.0e-9

isthmus_surface     skin voxels solid
surf_flux           skin kinetic/theory pressure 50.0 temperature 5000.0 &
                      mole-fraction 1.0 molecular-mass 5.31352e-26 reaction-prob 1.0 &
                      solid-mass-per-hit 3.98885e-26 mass-courant 0.8 select all
voxel_ablate        solid surface skin policy carryover/normal delete yes
iac_run             1

iac_verify          surface-mass-courant exact "0.8" tolerance 1.0e-12 absolute
